# absoluteDifference

- _absoluteDifference(x, y)_

Answer the absolute difference between _x_ and _y_.

```
>>> absoluteDifference(3, 5)
2

>>> (3 - 5, (3 - 5).abs)
(-2, 2)

>>> absoluteDifference(5, 3)
2

>>> (5 - 3, (5 - 3).abs)
(2, 2)
```

`absDif` is an alias for `absoluteDifference`.

* * *

See also: -, abs, subtract

